author: AIdan73
title: goofy
review: this set comes in a well presented package. the three minifigures are printed with alot of detail with back, arm and leg prints. but Owen has a really weird set of expressions. and the baby dinosaur is a good addition as well.

author: ShadowWolfHount
title: Kinda disappointing
review:
Compare to the other 2018 bricktober packs, Owen and Claire doesn't look that interesting to get, least Claire have different clothes, Owen just have a different shirt, least he have an arm printing and we get different face printings along with goofy ones with Owen.

The baby Raptor you can easily get in two sets, would been nice to get a different printing.

Ian is pretty much the only one that is really worth getting from this, especially as this is currently the only thing to get him.

I think this pack would be a lot better if it have character that are unlikely to be seen or rare to see in future Jurassic sets, like Dennis Nedry and John Hammond.
